  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If a product’s battery swells or overheats, it falls under the seller’s contractual warranty. The battery must be replaced, and any resulting damage from an exploded battery should be repaired.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Important Note:</strong> You cannot ship a product with a swollen battery due to the risk of explosion. In cases where a swollen battery is suspected, customers will be directed to diagnose the issue at a local repair shop.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Procedure:</strong></span></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Diagnosis and Repair:</strong></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Customers will be provided with a maximum repair budget </span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Within the guidelines of the table at the end of the article</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Below the price paid for the device.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>If the repair cost is within the budget:</strong></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer proceeds with the repair.</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The repair cost will be refunded to the customer upon submission of the repair invoice</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The cost of repair will be invoiced to you</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>If the repair is not possible or its cost exceeds the budget:</strong></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer is asked to pay for the extraction of the swollen battery at the repair shop</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer will be fully refunded for both the item and the extraction cost.</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The device will be returned to you and you will be invoiced for the extraction cost (30€ maximum). </span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n</li></ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Post-Repair Actions recap:</strong></span></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: circle;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If the device can be repaired, you are responsible for covering the cost invoiced by the repair shop</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"list-style-type: circle;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If the device cannot be repaired, the product will be fully refunded and returned to you.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Conclusion:</strong> This process ensures customer safety and satisfaction while maintaining compliance with warranty obligations. Always prioritize safety when dealing with potentially hazardous battery issues.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 815px;height: 1189.63px;border-color: #000000;\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 67.5833px;\"><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 320.33px;\">\n<div>\n<p> </p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 225.868px;\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Screen</strong></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 226.024px;\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Battery</strong></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</th></tr><tr style=\"height: 48.7847px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 320.33px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;text-align: center;width: 110.382px;\">\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">EU</span></p>\n</div>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;text-align: center;width: 101.597px;\">\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">US</span></p>\n</div>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;text-align: center;width: 110.382px;\">\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">EU</span></p>\n</div>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;text-align: center;width: 101.753px;\">\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">US</span></p>\n</div>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 48.784